Body: Description: We need to switch a group of computers to a new EPP department that has different settings. When we uninstall the original client, and install the new client, it still retains the old department code.

What We've Learned Updated: Used: http://download.endpointprotector.com/debug_agent/epp_uninstall.zip  to uninstall.
We reinstalled the branded client and it worked.
Next Steps Updated: Waiting 1 week for customer to update department for more computers.
